  description: "Tr\xFCmmerfrauen was an all-female West German New Wave (NDW) and
    Post-Punk band formed in 1980 in Ludwigshafen and associated with the Mannheim
    punk scene.  The group consisted of Stephanie Groth (guitar, vocals), Ingrid
    Janowsky (bass, vocals), Gabi Streckfuss (synthesizer, vocals), and initially
    Pia Lenz (drums). "
